readable.content: A man in a red jacket and khaki pants is walking through a part of what looks like Arizona . A man wearing jeans and a hooded , long sleeved top , and a backpack , walks in a desert . A person with a red hooded jacket and a black backpack is walking near a rocky wall . Man wearing red looks on at desert There is a lone hiker in the middle of a prairie with his back to the camera , showing his backpack .
